Camoflage::

She flipped a few more times. At the last flip, she lost her balance. 
She slipped and landed on her shoulder. At the point of impact with 
the floor, a small compartment opened up and out fell 6 little black 
cubes. Each about 1 inch by one inch. Cam got up and smiled up at 
Windlord. "Sorry, lost my balance."  she looked down and saw the 
cubes. "Uh oh. Your not supposed to see those." She grabbed them 
quickly and put them back in her shoulder compartment.
